# API keys for OpenAI / Anthropic / Google providers.
# Place actual 64-character hex keys here, one per line, OR as a Python list.
# The key loader (rescore_v6.py:_load_api_keys) extracts any 64-hex-char
# tokens it finds, so any plain-text or Python-dict layout works.
#
# Multiple keys are supported for round-robin parallelism; the asynchronous
# client pool will distribute requests across them. CONCURRENT_PER_KEY
# (env var, default 10) controls per-key concurrency.
#
# DO NOT commit real keys to a public repository. Add this file to your
# local .gitignore.
#
# Example:
# 0123456789abcdef0123456789abcdef0123456789abcdef0123456789abcdef
# fedcba9876543210fedcba9876543210fedcba9876543210fedcba9876543210
